import React from "react"; import "./footer.css"; import "../../App.css"; import "../../../src/ar-style.css"; import { useTranslation } from "react-i18next"; const Footer = () => { const { t } = useTranslation(); const getTranslatedArray = (key) => { const translation = t(key, { returnObjects: true }); return Array.isArray(translation) ? translation : []; }; return (
{/* Logo and Description */}

{t("footer.description")}

{/* Useful Links */}
{t("footer.usefulLinks.title")}
    {getTranslatedArray("footer.usefulLinks.items").map((link, index) => (
  • {link}
    • ))}
{/* Categories */}
{t("footer.categories.title")}
    {getTranslatedArray("footer.categories.items").map((category, index) => (
  • {category}
    • ))}
{/* Our Services */}
{t("footer.ourServices.title")}
    {getTranslatedArray("footer.ourServices.items").map((service, index) => (
  • {service}
    • ))}
{/* Support */}
{t("footer.support.title")}

{t("footer.support.location")}

{t("footer.support.phone")}

{t("footer.support.whatsapp")}

{t("footer.support.email")}

{/* Social Media Links */}
{t("footer.followUs")}
{[ { label: "Facebook", icon: "facebook-icon", background: "#1877F2", href: "#!" }, { label: "LinkedIn", icon: "linkedin-icon", background: "#0077B5", href: "#!" }, { label: "Instagram", icon: "instagram-icon", background: "linear-gradient(45deg, #F58529, #DD2A7B, #8134AF, #515BD4)", href: "#!" }, { label: "Twitter", icon: "twitter-icon", background: "#1DA1F2", href: "#!" }, { label: "TikTok", icon: "tiktok-icon", background: "#000000", href: "#!" }, { label: "YouTube", icon: "youtube-icon", background: "#FF0000", href: "#!" }, { label: "Pinterest", icon: "pinterest-icon", background: "#E60023", href: "#!" } ].map((social, index) => ( ))}

); }; export default Footer;
